txt.en: You have encountered the threatening Gundrágh. Guided by his handlers, Gundrágh patrols the path between the Morgul Vale and Osgiliath for intruders.
Gundrágh can be found patrolling Southern Ithilien.\n\nYou have encountered Gundrágh and should defeat the beast for the good of the Rangers in Southern Ithilien.
You have defeated Gundrágh and the beast's warband.
